HEADWORD: Homeling
<hw>Home"ling</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person or thing
belonging to a home or to a particular country; a native; <as>as, a word
which is a <ex>homeling</ex></as>.</def> <rj><au>Trench.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

